title: MENIFEE: Shooting at McDonald's; one dead, suspect in custody
text:
AARON CLAVERIE / STAFF WRITER
Published: Oct. 9, 2015 Updated: 8:28 p.m. MENIFEE: Shooting at McDonald's; one dead, suspect in custody Print Photo Share Pin It More Galleries ADVERTISEMENT Related article Â» A shooting inside the McDonald's restaurant on Bradley Road in Menifee left one man dead, police said Friday.
The shooting was reported around 6 p.m., said Deputy Armando Munoz. A suspect is in custody.
"There is no threat to public safety," he said.
This story is developing. Check back later for more details.
